import React from 'react'
import { Divider, Grid, Typography } from '@mui/material'

import TextField from '@mui/material/TextField'
const Contact = () => {
  return (
    <>
      <Typography align="center" variant="h5">
        Contact Me
      </Typography>{' '}
      <Divider variant="middle" style={{ backgroundColor: '#4dabf5' }} />
      <Grid container>
        <TextField
          id="standard-basic"
          label="Standard"
          variant="your name please"
        />
        <TextField
          id="standard-basic"
          label="Standard"
          variant="your email please"
        />
      </Grid>
    </>
  )
}

export default Contact
